title: Caribbean Jerk Inspired Chicken Traybake with Pepper and Green Beans
description: Our Caribbean Jerk Inspired Chicken Traybake captures the vibrant flavours of the Caribbean. Flavoured with jerk seasoning that contains paprika, cayenne, pimento and thyme, sweetness, spice and heat deliciously collide together.
